flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B{Downgrade list ready?}
    B -- No --> C[Request packages + target versions]
    B -- Yes --> D[Review availability + risk summary]
    D --> E{Security/policy concerns?}
    E -- Yes --> F[Require waiver/override]
    E -- No --> G{Approve downgrade batch?}
    F --> G
    G -- No --> H[Cancel; request adjustments]
    G -- Yes --> I[Trigger downgrades]
    I --> J{Completed?}
    J -- Yes --> K[Notify success; log pinned versions]
    J -- No --> L[Notify failures; assign follow-up]
    K --> M([Done])
    L --> M

